          Professional customer experience management
        </h2>
        <p>
          Since 2015, I've continued to hone my skills around customer service
          as a digital experience leader in the outdoor brand industry.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="cv-fr-content cv-fr-content-3">
        <h2 class="cv-fr-content-heading">A return to roots</h2>
        <p class="p-block">
          I'm eager to get out from behind a desk and work in an energizing food
          and beverage service role.
        </p>
        <p class="p-block">I have flexible part-time availability.</p>
        <p class="p-block">
